Textmate bundles:

1) Installing a bundle

  1) cd ~/Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles
  2) git clone git://github.com/Alshie/html-ipsum.git HTMLIpsum.tmbundle
  3) restart TextMate or Reload Bundles
  
2) Updating a bundle

  1) cd ~/Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles
  2) cd HTMLIpsum.tmbundle
  3) git pull